WEBVTT

00:00.634 --> 00:02.651
You can go ahead, rodney.

00:03.021 --> 00:05.352
- I don't remember where to start.
- Sure you do.

00:05.531 --> 00:06.281
No.

00:06.328 --> 00:10.570
Start with your name like we've been doing, okay, and we'll just go from there.

00:10.969 --> 00:12.152
My name...

00:12.270 --> 00:14.977
my name is...

00:15.434 --> 00:16.980
Mr.Rodney mckay.

00:17.016 --> 00:17.824
No...

00:17.848 --> 00:18.680
yes.

00:18.738 --> 00:21.539
Come on, now. You're Dr.Mckay, remember?

00:21.562 --> 00:23.883
No, I'm-- I'm not anymore.

00:23.884 --> 00:27.760
I'm not s-s-smart anymore.

00:27.842 --> 00:31.123
Doctors are smart, so I'm mister now.

00:31.252 --> 00:32.634
Okay.

00:34.979 --> 00:37.780
I used to be the smartest person ever...

00:37.885 --> 00:40.956
and-- and now... now I'm not.

00:40.999 --> 00:43.906
That's what we're trying to fix, right?

00:44.140 --> 00:45.499
No, you can't fix me.

00:45.500 --> 00:47.667
You know we're trying our very best--

00:47.726 --> 00:49.988
no, you can'T. You can'T.

00:49.989 --> 00:51.007
it's okay, rodney,

00:51.008 --> 00:52.824
what's the next thing you're supposed to say?

00:52.825 --> 00:54.945
Where... where did john go?

00:55.027 --> 00:56.667
He just had to go away for a few minutes. He'll be back--

00:56.668 --> 00:57.898
- john!
- Rodney...

00:58.619 --> 01:00.131
rodney, I'm your friend, I'm right here.

01:00.132 --> 01:02.439
Where are you, john?

01:03.260 --> 01:04.537
John!

01:08.666 --> 01:11.795
Why the hell didn't you tell me my brother was this far gone?

01:12.182 --> 01:13.576
It's happened pretty fast, jeannie.

01:13.611 --> 01:15.064
No, I...

01:15.557 --> 01:18.709
I got a message from him just a couple of weeks ago.

01:18.826 --> 01:21.779
he seemed perfectly fine. He'd never been so nice.

01:22.107 --> 01:25.799
That would have been shortly after he became infected.

01:26.830 --> 01:28.564
I didn't recognize the symptoms in time.

01:28.576 --> 01:30.416
It's not your fault, doc.

01:30.486 --> 01:32.514
Frankly, mrs. Miller,

01:32.607 --> 01:36.791
 we contacted you as soon as we became aware of the seriousness of his condition.

01:37.095 --> 01:42.205
In fact, daedalus dropped you off at the first available gate in pegasus because we were concerned that

01:42.299 --> 01:44.666
you wouldn't make it here in time.

01:45.275 --> 01:49.799
We thought you deserved a chance to say goodbye.

